{"tid":1394902,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華取消生日會 歌迷感愕然","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T08:29:29.000Z","uid":12558,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1a5c611b04b4a782014a83f6bcf7a9027685c6e0","tid":1394902,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"劉德華向來視他的歌迷為家人，每年都會提早舉行生日會，與一眾「家人」齊齊慶祝。以往劉華攜帶朱麗倩及女兒出席，可見劉華對歌迷會的「家人」多重視。<br />\n<br />\n不過，今年劉華就決定取消生日會，但沒有透露因，歌迷會亦已安排退款事宜。不少人得悉消息之後，大感失望，但仍支持劉華的決定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQVSNA2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQVSNA2.png&h=d526629e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0add356cdc9cc532a0bef70589226f50f9e934e","tid":1394902,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"多謝華仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d26e10b259c0c36fe1811c4aaf3e6389e77c15","tid":1394902,"uid":35014,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3496ba07fdbe81f909d4bb96e75c08e176c37d9","tid":1394902,"uid":12628,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:58:40.000Z","msg":"家人，肉麻到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得交會費"},{"pid":"e1b13599a73191223613cc5b25845e75828fe281","tid":1394902,"uid":1067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:01:21.000Z","msg":"支持家人嘅錢全部攞去填海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344e2776cbddc19ab336412cf9d1526c4314a7c4","tid":1394902,"uid":81312,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:02:34.000Z","msg":"填海華？"},{"pid":"b53b5ae370a3e16eb9645a082f77574fb8127f64","tid":1394902,"uid":33668,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"cit